 class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 22, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sra1665702688552.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sra1665702688552.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sra1665702688552.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sra1665702688552\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"sra1665702688552___areaframes__471896\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The [areaframes] section of the initialization file contains logical widget definitions for frames in Form components.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"sra1665702688552__topic_d144692e1_d144693e1_d144694e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sra1665702688552__p_d144695e1_d144696e1_d144697e1\">Each entry in this section has the following syntax:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sra1665702688552__p_d144698e1_d144699e1_d144700e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalFrameName</var>{<var class=\"keyword varname\">.ComponentName</var>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">=uframe(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Properties</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"sra1665702688552__section_w2880ab1b5b5_w2881ab1b5_w2882ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sra1665702688552__p_d144701e1_d144702e1_d144703e1\">Example:</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section pre\" id=\"sra1665702688552__section_w2883ab1b5b7_w2884ab1b5_w2885ab1\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[areaframes]\nframestyle1=uframe(bordertype=flat;forecolor=red;borderradius=20px)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section ul\" id=\"sra1665702688552__section_w2886ab1b5b9_w2887ab1b5_w2888ab1\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sra1665702688552__li_d50423e1_d50424e1_d50425e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalFrameName</var>—the name of the frame configuration.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sra1665702688552__li_d50426e1_d50427e1_d50428e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>—name of a component in which the named frame is defined.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sra1665702688552__li_d50429e1_d50430e1_d50431e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Properties</var>—semi-colon separated string of property-value pairs. The maximum length is 1024 characters.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"sra1665702688552__section_w2889ab1b5c11_w2890ab1b5_w2891ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Frame Widget Style Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\"> Physical Property Name </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\"> Property </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Attach</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bou1665702610816.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bou1665702610816.html\" title=\"The Attach to Window Border (Attach) widget property attaches the widget (or area frame) to one or more form window borders or split bars at runtime. This allows the element to be resized or moved when the window is resized or a split bar moved.\">Attach to Window Border (attach)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BorderType</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cys1665702610904.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cys1665702610904.html\" title=\"The BorderType property is used to display a flat or grooved border around an area frame, grid, or the default entity widget.\">BorderType</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BorderRadius</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gkz1665702610994.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gkz1665702610994.html\" title=\"The BorderRadius property causes the border of the area frame or entity to have rounded corners. The degree of rounding is determined by the value of the property.\">Border Radius (BorderRadius)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1 sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n                        Color Properties \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackColor</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwc1665702587483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwc1665702587483.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the object.\">Background Color (BackColor)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">ForeColor</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rbp1665702587714.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rbp1665702587714.html\" title=\"Color to use as the foreground (usually the text color).\">Foreground Color (ForeColor)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BorderColor</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mux1665702611074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mux1665702611074.html\" title=\"The BorderColor property displays a border of the specified color around the area frame or entity. It is applicable only if the BorderType property is flat.\">Border Color (BorderColor)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackColorFill</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lpd1665702587794.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lpd1665702587794.html\" title=\"Determines whether the background color is styled with a flat or gradient color.\">Gradient Fill Style (BackColorFill)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackcolorStart</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kto1665702611220.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kto1665702611220.html\" title=\"The BackColorStart widget property determines the color used at the start of a gradient background in an area frame for entity. The default is white.\">Gradient Color Start (BackColorStart)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">GradientStart</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mat1665702611295.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mat1665702611295.html\" title=\"The GradientStart property defines the edge of the area frame or entity from which to start shading the gradient background color. The shading ends at the opposite side.\">Gradient Start ( GradientStart)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">DropShadowColor</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ecy1665702611370.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ecy1665702611370.html\" title=\"The DropShadowColor property causes the area frame or entity to be displayed with a 4-pixel shadow of the specified color to the right and bottom of the object.\">Drop Shadow Color ( DropShadowColor)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" colspan=\"2\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1 sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n                        Background Image Properties \n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">BackImage</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"scc1665702611448.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/scc1665702611448.html\" title=\"Image used as background for the application window, form, or entity. This property can be set in ProcScript.\">Background Image (BackImage)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Halign</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kmv1665702611521.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kmv1665702611521.html\" title=\"This property determines how the data (text or image) is aligned in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Horizontal Alignment (Halign)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Valign</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gvp1665702611605.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gvp1665702611605.html\" title=\"This property determines the vertical alignment of data (text or image) in the widget, entity, area frame, or window.\">Vertical Alignment ( Valign)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Hscale</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbd1665702611680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbd1665702611680.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is horizontally scaled; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">Vscale</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sup1665702611757.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sup1665702611757.html\" title=\"This property determines how the image is scaled vertically; valid only for Image data types. Default value is 100 (percent).\">Vertical Scaling ( Vscale)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword\">PreserveAspect</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sra1665702688552__table_d17585e1_d17586e1_d17587e1__entry__2\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yxe1665702611833.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yxe1665702611833.html\" title=\"Determines whether the aspect ratio of the image is preserved at all times. True (default) or False.\">Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect)</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sra1665702688552__topic_d103697e1_d103698e1_d103699e1_d103700e1_d103701e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d296937e500\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sra1665702688552__p_d144707e1_d144708e1_d144709e1\">Area frame logical widgets are user-defined. The properties defined for each logical widget are applied to any area frame whose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Widget Type</span> property matches the <var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalFrameName</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sra1665702688552__p_d144710e1_d144711e1_d144712e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ujj1665702610581.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ujj1665702610581.html\" title=\"Area frames are objects that can be used to group or separate the contents of a Form component.\">Area Frames and Lines</a>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3610225\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3610225\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "[areaframes] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The [areaframes] section of the initialization file contains logical widget definitions for frames in Form components. Each entry in this section has the following syntax: LogicalFrameName { .ComponentName } =uframe( Properties ) Example: [areaframes] framestyle1=uframe(bordertype=flat;forecolor=red;borderradius=20px) Copy LogicalFrameName —the name of the frame configuration. ComponentName —name of a component in which the named frame is defined. Properties —semi-colon separated string of property-value pairs. The maximum length is 1024 characters. Table 1. Frame Widget Style Properties Physical Property Name Property Attach Attach to Window Border (attach) BorderType BorderType BorderRadius Border Radius (BorderRadius) Color Properties BackColor Background Color (BackColor) ForeColor Foreground Color (ForeColor) BorderColor Border Color (BorderColor) BackColorFill Gradient Fill Style (BackColorFill) BackcolorStart Gradient Color Start (BackColorStart) GradientStart Gradient Start ( GradientStart) DropShadowColor Drop Shadow Color ( DropShadowColor) Background Image Properties BackImage Background Image (BackImage) Halign Horizontal Alignment (Halign) Valign Vertical Alignment ( Valign) Hscale Horizontal Scaling ( Hscale) Vscale Vertical Scaling ( Vscale) PreserveAspect Preserve Aspect Ratio ( PreserveAspect) Description Area frame logical widgets are user-defined. The properties defined for each logical widget are applied to any area frame whose Widget Type property matches the LogicalFrameName . For more information, see Area Frames and Lines . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}